s every 8 hours at 00:00, 08:00, and 16:00 UTC using a time-weighted average of the premium/discount between perpetual and mark prices. The funding rate is capped at ±0.75% per interval, with payments exchanged directly between long and short position holders. Bybit's unified trading account allows seamless cross-margining between spot MATIC holdings and perpetual positions for efficient arbitrage execution."}]]}],"$Lf",["$L10","$L11","$L12"],"$L13"]}],"$L14"]}]]}]
